28 SECTION 8. Chapter 148 of the General Laws, as appearing in the 2022 Official
29 Edition, is hereby amended by striking sections 19 to 20B, inclusive, and inserting in place
30 thereof the following sections:-
31 Section 19. No person shall conduct blasting operations unless such person has applied
32 for and obtained a certificate of competency issued by the marshal. Any person wishing to
33 obtain said certificate shall make application on a form approved by the marshal. A fee set
